The paper focuses on adapting and evaluating a deep learning language model for answering why-questions based on patient-specific clinical text. This falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning, which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category as it specifically deals with NLP. cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely as they cover the broader field of machine learning, which includes NLP. cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possibility as the paper deals with clinical text and has implications for healthcare. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possibility as the paper deals with extracting information from clinical text.
